Megatron kneeled, with one hand firmly clutching Triggerhappy, with the
other he pointed towards his lost fusion cannon. "Retrieve my cannon
Blowpipe." He ordered. He then stood up, the joints in his arms tensing
as he pulled Triggerhappy up with him, slinging another Decepticon over
his shoulder.
